
<p>You can apply a drop shadow filter using the <code>filter-drop-shadow</code> component.</p>

<p>You can place the filter in the svg shape component's block:</p>

<pre><code>&#123;&#123;#svg-triangle size="100" filter="inline-drop-shadow" class="green"&#125;&#125;
  &#123;&#123;filter-drop-shadow id="inline-drop-shadow" dx="2" dx="4"&#125;&#125;
&#123;&#123;/svg-triangle&#125;&#125;</code></pre>

<p>You can also use an <code>{{link-to 'svg-filters' 'svg-filters'}}</code> component to hold a collection of filters.</p>

<div align="center">
  {{#svg-triangle size="100" filter="inline-drop-shadow" class="green"}}
    {{filter-drop-shadow id="inline-drop-shadow" dx="2" dy="4"}}
  {{/svg-triangle}}
</div>
